Package: biomAid
Title: Biometric Tools for Multi-Environment Plant Breeding Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("J", "Taylor", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "j.taylor@example.com")
Description: Provides biometric tools for analysing multi-environment plant
    breeding trials fitted with ASReml-R V4 mixed models. Includes functions
    for multiple comparison criteria (HSD, LSD, Bonferroni), Wald tests on
    fixed-effect contrasts, Factor Analytic Selection Tools (FAST) and
    interaction class (iClass) analysis, multivariate random and fixed
    regression of treatment BLUPs/BLUEs, and simulation of multi-treatment
    multi-environment trial data.
